OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,6,Fshowery rain in the north in the
OL,7,Fmorning but drier elsewhere. A drier
OL,8,Fand brighter afternoon with a few
OL,9,Fshowers possible for all parts, which
OL,10,Fmay be heavy. Light or moderate
OL,11,Fnortheasterly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA mostly cloudy and dry
OL,14,Fevening but an isolated shower
OL,15,Fpossible, clear spells for the Isles.
OL,16,FDry overnight with clear intervals.
OL,17,FMostly light easterly winds but breezy
OL,18,Fnear the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
